==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sevenfold
<hw>Sev"en*fold`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Repeated seven
times; having seven thicknesses; increased to seven times the size or
amount.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Sevenfold</xex> rage.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sevenfold</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Sevenfold
<hw>Sev"en*fold`</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Seven times as much or as
often.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Whosoever slayeth Cain, vengeance shall be taken on him
<qex>sevenfold</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Gen. iv. 15.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sevennight</ent>⟦br⟧
